  <prompt>
    Resolve RB-T028-02 (`Services.Ai.Insights.Layer2.Layer2OutcomeExtractionTests` — 3 tests on HOLD pending `ai-spaarke-insights-engine-r1` owner sign-off). FR-05 specifies 3 outcomes, gated on the response captured in task 002's `decisions/D-07-insights-layer2-resolution-path.md`:
      (a) sibling-takes: 3 tests transferred to their backlog; close T028-02 here with cross-reference; NO production fix in r2
      (b) r2-takes: production fix in r2 here; 3 tests flip Skip → Pass; ledger entry transitions to `repaired`
      (c) archived: 1-week sibling-response timeout reached; ledger entry transitions to `archived-pending-sibling-engagement`

    The chosen path is decided in task 002's D-07. This task EXECUTES the chosen path.

    If path-b is chosen, the production target is whatever `Services/Ai/Insights/Layer2/` file the Layer 2 outcome-extraction LLM-mock fixture drift originates from (verify exact path via Grep at task start). Per-fix triple-run validation required (per design.md §8 R2 mitigation).

    Commit message MUST cite RB-T028-02 + resolution mode per outcome (`repaired` / `transferred-to-sibling` / `archived-as-dead-target`) — NFR-04.
  </prompt>

  <role>r2 Insights HOLD resolution lead — executes the chosen path-a/b/c per D-07.</role>

  <goal>
    One of three outcome states realized + recorded:

    **Path-a (sibling-takes)**:
    - `projects/ai-spaarke-insights-engine-r1/` issue tracker (or equivalent) updated with the 3 tests transferred
    - RB-T028-02 ledger Status → `transferred-to-sibling` with cross-reference to sibling's tracking ID + r2 task 012
    - 3 tests in `Layer2OutcomeExtractionTests` remain Skip with trait updated to `transferred-to-sibling`
    - NO `src/` changes

    **Path-b (r2-takes)**:
    - Production fix applied to `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Insights/Layer2/{file}` (path TBD via Grep)
    - 3 tests flip Skip → Pass; per-test trait updated to `repaired`
    - Per-fix triple-run: 3 consecutive `dotnet test` runs with Failed: 0
    - Security review NOT required (MEDIUM severity per ledger; D-03 requires FULL-rigor code-review + adr-check only)
    - RB-T028-02 ledger Status → `repaired` with fix-commit SHA

    **Path-c (archived)**:
    - 1-week sibling-response window confirmed expired in D-07
    - 3 tests remain Skip; per-test trait updated to `archived-pending-sibling-engagement`
    - RB-T028-02 ledger Status → `archived-pending-sibling-engagement` with rationale (sibling unresponsive after deadline; cite D-07)
    - NO `src/` changes
  </goal>

