  <context>
    <background>
      RB-T028-02 (Layer 2 outcome-extraction LLM-mock fixture drift) was filed by r1 with a special HOLD status: r1's repair-not-rewrite mandate could not resolve a sibling-project-owned domain. The 3 affected tests live in `Services.Ai.Insights.Layer2.Layer2OutcomeExtractionTests` and exercise the Insights pipeline Layer-2 boundary. The fix path depends on whether `ai-spaarke-insights-engine-r1` owns the bug or whether r2 (BFF surface) should absorb it.

      Task 002 dispatched outreach to the Insights sibling owner with a 1-week response window. Task 012's outcome path is determined by D-07 (sibling-takes / r2-takes / archived). This task executes whichever path D-07 chose; the choice is NOT made here.

      If path-b is chosen, the production target is likely in `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Insights/Layer2/` — but exact file is discovered via Grep at task start (the fixture-drift root cause may be in `OutcomeExtractor.cs` / `LayerCoordinator.cs` / `Layer2Service.cs` or similar; verify before editing).
    </background>
    <dependencies>
      <dependency task="002" status="must-complete-first">D-07 decision must be in place before task 012 executes; if D-07 still draft (response pending), task 012 waits</dependency>
    </dependencies>
  </context>

  <relevant-files>
    <file>projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/decisions/D-07-insights-layer2-resolution-path.md</file>
    <file>projects/sdap-bff.api-test-suite-repair/ledgers/real-bug-ledger.md</file>
    <file>tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/Insights/Layer2/Layer2OutcomeExtractionTests.cs</file>
    <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Insights/Layer2/</file>
  </relevant-files>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read `projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/decisions/D-07-insights-layer2-resolution-path.md`. Confirm the chosen path (a/b/c). If D-07 is still draft (no response received yet), HOLD this task until task 002's 1-week response window closes.</step>
    <step order="2">Read RB-T028-02 entry in `projects/sdap-bff.api-test-suite-repair/ledgers/real-bug-ledger.md` end-to-end; identify the 3 cited Skipped tests in `Layer2OutcomeExtractionTests.cs`.</step>
    <step order="3">**IF path-a (sibling-takes)**: (a) File the 3 tests as an issue in `ai-spaarke-insights-engine-r1` tracker (or equivalent); capture tracking ID. (b) Update the 3 tests in `Layer2OutcomeExtractionTests.cs`: per-test trait `[Trait("status","real-bug-pending-fix")]` → `[Trait("status","transferred-to-sibling")]`; Skip messages updated to cite sibling tracking ID. (c) RB-T028-02 ledger Status → `transferred-to-sibling`. (d) Skip to step 7.</step>
    <step order="4">**IF path-c (archived)**: (a) Verify D-07 confirms response window expired. (b) Update the 3 tests: trait → `archived-pending-sibling-engagement`; Skip messages updated to cite rationale. (c) RB-T028-02 ledger Status → `archived-pending-sibling-engagement`. (d) Skip to step 7.</step>
    <step order="5">**IF path-b (r2-takes)**: Grep `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Insights/Layer2/` for outcome-extraction logic; identify the LLM-mock fixture-drift root cause file. Apply the production fix per the ledger entry's recommended fix. Build: `dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/` — 0 errors.</step>
    <step order="6">**IF path-b**: Update the 3 tests in `Layer2OutcomeExtractionTests.cs`: remove Skip; trait → `repaired`. Run `dotnet test --filter "FullyQualifiedName~Layer2OutcomeExtractionTests"`; confirm all 3 pass. Per-fix triple-run: `dotnet test tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/ --logger trx` 3 consecutive runs; Failed: 0 across all 3. RB-T028-02 ledger Status → `repaired` with fix-commit SHA.</step>
    <step order="7">For all paths: run Step 9.5 quality gates (`code-review` + `adr-check`) if path-b; gates skipped if path-a or path-c (no `src/` change).</step>
    <step order="8">Commit message: cite RB-T028-02 + resolution mode per chosen path (`repaired` / `transferred-to-sibling` / `archived-as-dead-target`). Reference D-07 + FR-05.</step>
    <step order="9">Update `projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/tasks/TASK-INDEX.md` — mark 012 as ✅ with outcome path annotation; update `current-task.md`.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="Read">D-07 decision, ledger, test file</tool>
    <tool name="Grep">If path-b: locate Layer 2 outcome-extraction source file</tool>
    <tool name="Edit">Update test attributes (all paths); apply production fix (path-b only)</tool>
    <tool name="Bash">If path-b: `dotnet build`, `dotnet test --filter`, `dotnet test --logger trx` (×3)</tool>
    <tool name="Write">Update ledger entry status</tool>
  </tools>

  <outputs>
    <output type="test">tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/Insights/Layer2/Layer2OutcomeExtractionTests.cs (3 tests updated per path)</output>
